loadFromCKB

public void loadFromCKB()
Loads data from the cellular knowledge base, which is a metadata warehouse. Once the metadata is sorted through, the raw data is retrieved from the CCDB and other sources.

load

public abstract void load()
Loads objects into the scene. Currently this is done manually mostly from files on the client. This is being transitioned to the loadFromCKB method where we are loading data from the cellular knowledge base
